Installation Instructions (2.x release)
 Download the software from the Downloads tab in the project web presence
 Un-tar it using TAR
        tar -xzf class-code-1.0.tar.gz 
 Change to the project directory
        cd class-code-2.0 
 Run the configure script -h will show you the build and install options
        ./configure 
 Make the code
        make 
 Install the code (in /usr/local/ if you didn't adjust --prefix=DIR
        make install 
